These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, sprite, tea
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, ferret, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
5. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | iced-tea | tea | sprite |
| Pet        | turtle | goldfish   | pony | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, drama, sports, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: british, thai, turkish, argentine
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the british is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the turkish is in an odd position##4
4. the british is the person watching romance movies##1
5. the thai is on the right of the turkish##1
6. the british is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | romance  | drama  | animation |
| Nationality   | argentine    | british | turkish | thai    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, orange, onion, tomato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, sports, zombie, horror
1. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person eating onion is in an even position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | tomato | onion | orange    | papaya      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | horror     | drama | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, fishing, baking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, trance, salsa, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the fan of metal and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | baking | chess | magic-tricks | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | metal   | trance    | jazz  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, funk, pop, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, turkish, colombian, japanese
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the japanese##1
2. the turkish is the fan of techno##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
5. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
6. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | trance    | pop   | techno       |
| Nationality   | brazilian | japanese | colombian | turkish |

