4. the australian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the russian is on the left or right of the australian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | disaster | drama | zombie |
| Nationality   | pakistani | american     | australian  | russian  |

