.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, adventure, sports
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, trike, bus, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | sports | adventure | animation    |
| Transport     | skateboard | bus  | bike     | trike |

