.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, journalist, designer, freelancer
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, hedgehog, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the journalist##3
2. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
4. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the librarian is between the freelancer and the journalist##2
6. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the hamster is between the librarian and the owner of the hedgehog##2
8. the librarian is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | journalist | librarian      | freelancer | designer |
| Pet   | turtle  | dog | hamster    | hedgehog            |

