.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, kiwi, lime, corn
4 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla, goldfish, guinea-pig
1. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating lime##2
4. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating lime is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | corn | kiwi   | peach | lime |
| Pet    | guinea-pig     | chinchilla | ferret     | goldfish  |

