.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, country, soul
1. the person drinking fanta is the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the fan of soul is between the fan of folk and the person drinking sprite##2
4. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | sprite   | fanta | water |
| Music-Genre   | country | hip-hop | soul        | folk    |

