.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, mirinda, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, tennis, rowing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola   | iced-tea   | coffee      | mirinda      |
| Sport      | tennis | rowing | skiing | basketball |

