.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, strawberry, cauliflower, pepper
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, pop, d&b, country
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
3. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the fan of pop and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper | strawberry  | cauliflower  | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | country  | d&b | electronic | pop   |

