.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, cooking, dancing, hiking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, badminton, handball
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | hiking | cooking         | rock-climbing   | dancing |
| Sport   | badminton    | surfing | handball | climbing   |

