.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, singing, cooking, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
5. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | chess | cooking    | drawing |
| Sport   | snowboarding   | skateboarding  | tennis | rowing     |

