.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, traveling, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, colombian, mexican, egyptian
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
3. the colombian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the mexican is on the left or right of the colombian##3
5. the colombian is between the egyptian and the mexican##2
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games   | traveling | drawing | fishing    |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian  | egyptian     | polish |

