.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, sprite, coffee
There 4 different types of food: pear, plum, cranberry, pineapple
1. the person eating plum is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4
7. the person eating pear is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade    | sprite       | cola |
| Food       | plum  | cranberry | pineapple | pear  |

