.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, british, indian, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, train, skateboard, bike
1. the chinese is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the indian##1
5. the chinese is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | british | indian | chinese  | spanish |
| Transport     | car      | skateboard       | train | bike     |

