.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dancer, journalist, police-officer
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bike, tram, motorbike
1. the dancer is in an even position##4
2. the dancer is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
3. the person driving the bike is between the coach and the person driving the ship##2
4. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the police-officer##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | coach | journalist   | police-officer | dancer |
| Transport   | motorbike          | bike | ship         | tram  |

 